{% comment %}
  b2b-price.liquid — Theme App Extension App Block
  Phase 1B implementation

  This block renders the tier-discounted price alongside (or replacing) the
  standard Shopify price on product pages. It reads the buyer's cached tier
  from localStorage (set after login by the storefront JS module) and applies
  the discount client-side for instant display.

  IMPORTANT — Security invariant (see DECISIONS #10):
  The localStorage tier cache is for UX only. It provides instant price
  display on subsequent page loads WITHOUT a server round-trip. The actual
  discount is always applied server-side by the cart-transform Shopify Function,
  which re-resolves the tier from the Company metafield on every request.
  Never use the localStorage cache to gate access or make authorization decisions.

  TODO Phase 1B:
  - Read tier_id from localStorage key 'b2b_tier'
  - Fetch tier discount config from App Proxy (/apps/b2b/tier?id=...)
  - Render discounted price with tier badge
  - Handle loading state and missing/expired cache gracefully
  - Respect CSP — no inline scripts; all JS in assets/b2b-price.js
{% endcomment %}

<div
  class="b2b-price-block"
  data-b2b-price-block
  data-product-id="{{ product.id }}"
  data-variant-id="{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.id }}"
  data-base-price="{{ product.selected_or_first_available_variant.price }}"
>
  {%- comment -%}
    Populated by assets/b2b-price.js after reading the tier from localStorage.
    Falls back gracefully to empty when no B2B session is active.
  {%- endcomment -%}
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "B2B Tier Price",
  "target": "section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "checkbox",
      "id": "show_savings_badge",
      "label": "Show savings badge",
      "default": true
    },
    {
      "type": "select",
      "id": "price_display",
      "label": "Price display mode",
      "options": [
        { "value": "replace", "label": "Replace standard price" },
        { "value": "alongside", "label": "Show alongside standard price" }
      ],
      "default": "alongside"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
